        "The invention of the computer",
        "The launch of the first robot",
      ],
      correctAnswer: "The Dartmouth Conference in 1956",
    },
    {
      question: "What breakthrough in AI occurred during the 2010s?",
      options: [
        "Advancements in Deep Learning and Neural Networks",
        "Invention of the internet",
        "Development of the first transistor",
      ],
      correctAnswer: "Advancements in Deep Learning and Neural Networks",
    },
    {
      question: "What is Narrow AI?",
      options: [
        "AI designed to perform a specific task.",
        "AI that mimics human intelligence entirely.",
        "AI that can surpass human intelligence.",
      ],
      correctAnswer: "AI designed to perform a specific task.",
    },
    {
      question: "What is the main difference between General AI and Super AI?",
      options: [
        "General AI equals human intelligence, Super AI surpasses it.",
        "General AI is task-specific, Super AI is task-agnostic.",
        "General AI is slower than Super AI.",
      ],
      correctAnswer:
        "General AI equals human intelligence, Super AI surpasses it.",
    },
    {
      question: "Which type of AI is widely used today?",
      options: ["Narrow AI", "General AI", "Super AI"],
      correctAnswer: "Narrow AI",
    },
    {
      question: "What is Narrow AI?",
      options: [
        "AI that can perform a single task or a narrow range of tasks.",
        "AI that is as intelligent as humans.",
        "AI that surpasses human intelligence.",
      ],
      correctAnswer:
        "AI that can perform a single task or a narrow range of tasks.",
    },
    {
      question:
        "Which of the following is an example of an AI application in manufacturing?",
      options: [
